data.description: Big, Bright & Beautiful! Executive level, two story home with fully finished walkout basement. Enjoy almost 3 acres of private, wooded land, overlooking a pond which attracts an abundance of diverse wildlife. Hardwood flooring throughout, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, radiant basement floor heat, Andersen 400 series windows/doors, central vacuum, just to name a few. Main lvl: a two-story foyer, formal living rm, dining rm with dry bar, kitchen, informal dining rm with deck access, two-story informal living rm with fireplace and exterior french doors, dining rm, 1/2 bath and laundry rm. Upper lvl: Primary bedroom with ensuite, 2 additional bedrooms and full bathroom. Lower lvl: Stained concrete floors, a 3/4 bath, family rm, entertainment space with patio access, leisure area/wet bar with island. Sprinkler system, boiler,  hydronic heat furnace. New roof '22, A/C '21, well pump '19, indirect water heater '22, pressure tank '18. Seller is  licensed Realtor.
